item.description:
I'm thinking Skewers on 38 in Tewksbury around 7 and head over to Callahans 8-8:30.

http://www.skewerswoodgrill.com/index.php
The key to our delicious food is our real wood grill. The intense heat of the fire brings out the natural flavors of our fresh meat and fish. In addition, we use staples of Mediterranean cooking such as olive oil, lemon and herbs to marinate our fish and meats. We guarantee consistently good food made from fresh, high-quality ingredients.
TJ Callahans is a local laid back hang out where you can dance as if no one was watching.

http://www.tjcallahanspub.com/
http://www.hitsquad.net/
